; qlfile -- qlot dependency manifest for mlisp
; Run: qlot install  (creates qlfile.lock + .qlot/ local environment)
; See: https://github.com/fukamachi/qlot
;
; Primary BDD/unit testing framework (used by 'make test-unit' / CI
; unit-tests job). The 'docs' CI job uses its own qlfile-template
; (inline in ci.yml) with an additional 'ultralisp 40ants-doc' line --
; 40ants-doc is not in the standard Quicklisp dist, and qlot's `ql`
; directive always resolves against the quicklisp dist regardless of
; any additional `dist` lines; the package-specific `ultralisp <pkg>`
; directive is required instead.

